      "widgets_values": [
        "Cute cartoon style for kids, 4x2 grid storyboard in 16:9 landscape aspect ratio, eight adorable sequential scenes featuring the same cheerful boy bunny, big floppy bunny ears, fluffy tail, wearing a white crop top that says \"AutoGrid\" in fun black font and black adidas shorts.\n\nTop row:\nPanel 1 (top-left): the boy bunny taking a cheerful front-facing selfie, smiling brightly with sparkly eyes while holding a purple phone.\nPanel 2: the boy bunny happily drawing in a sketchbook at a desk, looking focused and content.\nPanel 3: the boy bunny relaxing on a bed, lying on his back with a peaceful dreamy smile.\nPanel 4: the boy bunny taking a stylish mirror selfie, posing cutely and showing his fluffy tail.\n\nBottom row:\nPanel 5: the boy bunny swimming happily at the pool, splashing in the water with wet fur and big smile.\nPanel 6: the boy bunny happily eating pasta in a cozy restaurant, fork in hand with a satisfied expression.\nPanel 7: the boy bunny on a cute date with his bunny best friend, both smiling together at a café table.\nPanel 8 (bottom-right): the boy bunny teaching math in front of a blackboard, wearing cute glasses and writing the number 67 while explaining with a friendly smile.\n\nConsistent adorable boy bunny character design across all panels, fluffy details, vibrant colors, simple clean cartoon style for kids, bright joyful atmosphere, smooth linework, high detail, fun and wholesome, masterpiece kids cartoon illustration, clean 4x2 grid layout"
      ]
    },
